These are some very beautiful shoes. The detail on them is striking, along with extra support that make them good for[nbsp]running[nbsp]long distances.

These shoes say "Yeah, I could do that, but I don't want to." Let the overachievers have their fun in the sun. We're more than happy sitting back and watching them twist an ankle or something stupid. Then we can point and laugh.

Feel the burn. Push it to the max. No pain no gain. C'mon... One more rep. You can do it. What are, you, some sort of wimp? I bet you've never won anything in your entire life. Really? Prove it. Buy these shoes.

Does your kid have what it takes to be a professional athlete? Find out with these shoes. After wearing these shoes for 3 months the shoes will email you a report on whether or not your child has what it takes to be a pro. The sensitive electronic readouts measure strength, endurance, and gusto.
These shoes come with a free pedicure to make sure no one is grossed out by your toes.

These shoes come with a free pedicure to make sure no one is grossed out by your toes. Hey, admit it... Your toes aren't extremely appealing. These shoes will force you to take better care of them, though, because they will be out there for all the world to see. So cover up those corns, and abolish those[nbsp]bunions, because your toes are coming out to play.

These sandals come pre-filled with sand, just like walking on the beach. Every step gives you the sensation of almost stepping on some sharp seashell or possibly broken glass, along with the hotfoot of walking on scalding sand. Take a vacation every day with these fabulous sandals.
If everyone could just see through its macho exterior to the supple insole.

If everyone could just see through its macho exterior to the supple insole. This boot looks like it is ready to break open a can of whoop-ass, but really it just wants to cradle your feet in supple goodness. And if you make fun of them, then get ready for a stomping.
